These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, hiking, rock-climbing, collecting
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, thriller, spy, romance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, skiing, golf, skateboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, van, boat, roller
 1. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the person who's sport is surfing##8
 2. the person driving the helicopter is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
 3. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
 5. the person driving the helicopter is not to the right of the person driving the helicopter##8
 6. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
 8. the person watching romance movies is between the person driving the van and the person who's sport is skiing##2
 9. the person driving the roller is the person watching spy movies##1
10. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
11. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
13. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the person driving the roller##8
14. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person driving the boat##1
15. the person who's hobby is hiking is not the person who's sport is skiing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | drawing     | hiking   | collecting | rock-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | romance   | martial-arts   | spy  |
| Sport         | skiing  | golf  | skateboarding  | surfing |
| Transport     | helicopter    | boat | van     | roller    |

