.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, tea, cola, juice
There 4 different types of food: apricot, tomato, corn, cherry
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, soul, gospel, d&b
4 different pets are kept: snake, hamster, rat, ferret
 1. the fan of gospel is between the owner of the snake and the fan of soul##2
 2. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the owner of the hamster##8
 3. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
 5. the owner of the snake is not to the left of the fan of soul##8
 6. the person eating cherry is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
 7. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
 8. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of classical is the owner of the hamster##1
10. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
11. the owner of the snake is not to the left of the fan of gospel##8
12. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
13. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
14. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
15. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
17. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the fan of soul##8
18. the person eating tomato is not to the right of the owner of the hamster##8
19. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | cola | juice  | tea  |
| Food          | cherry     | tomato | apricot | corn  |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | gospel  | d&b | classical |
| Pet           | rat | ferret | snake    | hamster  |

