.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, gardening, traveling, cooking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, horror, animation, scientific
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, disco, punk, country
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, golf, skateboarding, soccer
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 2. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the fan of salsa##5
 5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person watching superhero movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is not to the left of the person watching animation movies##8
 7. the fan of punk is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
11. the person watching superhero movies is not to the left of the fan of disco##8
12. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | chess    | cooking   | traveling | gardening |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero     | animation  | scientific   | horror      |
| Music-Genre   | disco | salsa    | punk      | country       |
| Sport         | skateboarding    | ice-hockey | soccer   | golf    |

