 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
 6. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the right of the person eating lime##8
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
 9. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the police-officer##1
10. the freelancer is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
11. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the right of the person eating strawberry##8
12. the pilot is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
13. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
14. the freelancer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
