 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
 5. the person driving the motorbike is the french##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the malaysian##8
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is not the brazilian##6
 8. the dancer is somewhere between the person driving the motorbike and the person drinking almond-milk##7
 9. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the dancer##5
10. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the dancer##3
11. the entrepreneur is on the right of the fisherman##1
12. the dancer is not the turkish##6
13. the malaysian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
14. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
15. the person driving the trike is not to the right of the dancer##8

.:: Answer ::.
