 4. the photographer is the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the person drinking sprite is in an even position##4
 6. the person driving the train is somewhere between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking cola##7
 7. the person driving the train is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8
 8. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is sudoku##7
 9. the accountant is on the far left or far right##3
10. the dancer is not to the left of the dancer##8
11. the accountant is on the far left##1
12. the analyst is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the train is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
14. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
15. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
16. the dancer is not to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##8

.:: Answer ::.
