.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, juice, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, jazz, dubstep, r&b
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, skateboarding, ice-hockey
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, helicopter, car, skateboard
 1. the person drinking juice is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 2. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 3. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
 6. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
 7. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 8. the person driving the helicopter is not to the right of the person who's sport is handball##8
 9. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
10. the person drinking fanta is not to the right of the fan of jazz##8
11. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
12. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate   | lemonade     | juice    | fanta |
| Music-Genre   | punk  | r&b      | dubstep     | jazz     |
| Sport         | biathlon | skateboarding  | ice-hockey     | handball  |
| Transport     | train     | car | skateboard | helicopter     |

